The '''Esselian Hall''', also known as the '''Esselian parliament''' and simply as '''the Hall''',<ref name="ITCW">{{JournalCite|7|Into the Core Worlds}}</ref> was the governing body of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]] following the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="GatORW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref> It was led by a [[President/Legends|President]] and they met in the [[Hall of Esseles]] in [[Calamar]].

During the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Cambira Ralle]] served as president, although much power was lost to [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Griff Takel]]. Political factions of the Hall included the [[Forad Party|Forad]], [[Cardean Party|Cardean]], and [[Esselian New Order Party|Esselian New Order Parties]].

Following the [[Esselian Hall election, 2 ABY|election]] of [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the Forad Party lost its grip on the majority, with the Esselian New Order Party making major inroads.<ref name="GNN8">{{JournalCite|8|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref>

